verses:
Holy, holy, holy,
Holy is the Lord!
Holy, holy, holy,
Holy is our God!
He who always liveth,
Evermore the same
Heav'n and earth He ruleth,
Come and praise His name!

Holy, holy, holy,
Holy is the Lord!
Holy, holy, holy,
Holy is our God!
Glorious and beloved
Is the One adored!
Holy, holy, holy,
Holy is the Lord.
